\f2\b \cf2 Templates and the crucial data for performance\
\pard\pardeftab560\qj\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0 \cf2 \
\
Templates need metadata of type of projects. \
Software can store several templates into libraries, chained by types, that can be shared to the world. Attached is a document which contains a Typology BreakDown Structure, called \'93MetaFilePM\'94 which consists on a metadata for projects templates. This document is editable and should be the key to tidying up the history records of millions of future plans and executed projects.\
\
The goal is to provide this metadata as a toolKit to any project management software, as well as convert project plans or executed to a universal template, in order to be imported to any software as a service.\
Projects executed are extremely necessary as project templates because they give their lessons learned, plus the time executed compared with the time originally estimated. Like this, plans are important but are not tested. Execution gives all the actions and mistakes taken, fundamental to avoid any error when a similar package, or simple task is repeated.\
\
Types should not be confined to themes of project only. \
Inside the themes or in some cases transversally, there are other typologies to be considerer which are described on typical knowledge areas of Project Management like:\
\pard\pardeftab560\partightenfactor0
\cf2 Project Risks\
Project quality\
Project stakeholders\
Project time/schedule\
Project cost\
\pard\pardeftab560\qj\partightenfactor0
\cf2 but also, obviously by the size, members and their efforts\
Additionally, add the ratio with the organization or portofolio. This last type refers directly to the environment culture. Explaining, if the company works only on scientific high research where certainty is very uncommon, a project that is very risky won\'92t necessary be more considerer than other projects. The opposite happens if the company is e.g. a Bank or Insurance company, where stability is a requirement and if the project is too risky, double efforts on concerns will be made.\
\
As summary, templates of project execution give us background, and this background also prepare the future by the metrical data of the performance of the project. Of course, this executions need to be well documented, in an universal form that can be escalate to many other scenarios.\
